chat_history.content:
I'm sorry, I couldn't find a clear list of the four most expensive elements, but I did find some information on the most expensive elements by weight and a list of the rarest elements.

## Most Expensive Elements by Weight
- Rhodium ($27,000 per kilogram)
- Platinum ($29,000 per kilogram)
- Iridium ($17,000 per kilogram)
- Gold ($56,000 per kilogram)

## Rarest Elements
1. Astatine - Discovered in 1940
2. Meitnerium - Discovered in 1982
3. Roentgenium - Discovered in 1994
4. Copernicium - Discovered in 1996
